compactReports.title: Excessive Heat Warning
compactReports.area: Central Siskiyou County; Western Siskiyou County
compactReports.detail: ...VERY HOT TEMPERATURES WILL PERSIST INTO FRIDAY... .Temperatures will be dangerously hot through Friday. There will be little relief overnight with temperatures remaining much warmer than normal. High temperatures on Friday will still be above 100 at most valleys west of the Cascades. ...EXCESSIVE HEAT WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM PDT
compactReports.summary: Excessive Heat Warning issued August 03 at 2:12PM PDT until August 04 at 8:00PM PDT by NWS
